text.paragraph:
Adalimumab has been studied in 464 adult subjects with uveitis (UV) in placebo-controlled and open-label extension studies and in 90 pediatric subjects with uveitis (Study PUV-I) [see Clinical Studies (14.10

                           , 14.11

                           )]. The safety profile for subjects with UV treated with adalimumab was similar to the safety profile seen in subjects with RA.
